{"tid":1703674,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新巴工會呼籲會員注意安全","createTime":"2019-11-10T11:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T15:51:30.000Z","uid":63979,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"693176b8183bb4dd8391586ea1530ea1e2c97425","tid":1703674,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:27:36.000Z","msg":"致各位會員：<br />\n<br />\n鑑於明天有市民發起三罷及堵塞行動，本會現呼籲各位會員如果明天於道路上遇上路障，請耐心等候及向控制中心報告，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有即時危險請疏散乘客及棄車離開</span>，注意安全。<br />\n<br />\n如各位會員身體不適、或於上班路途有問題，請跟足程序通知公司。<br />\n<br />\n新世界第一巴士職工會<br />\n2019年11月10日<br />\n<br />\n#三罷 #注意安全 #大型路障<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/579355445500005/posts/2159712014130999?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F579355445500005%2Fposts%2F2159712014130999%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=8d86326b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/579355445500005/posts/2159712014130999?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位唔知點理解呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6c03ca948eb6173906e8dabdec678c7f11a795","tid":1703674,"uid":79793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:30:53.000Z","msg":"棄車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e9ee8db68f90e7bbc1e410691d1ec859314e8a","tid":1703674,"uid":268619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"聽日唔會有巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe837f54a835f758e753b9418106db889db9444","tid":1703674,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgm